    "longBusinessSummary": "An Cuong Wood - Working Joint Stock Company manufactures and trades in wooden household products, industrial wooden items, artificial boards, interior decoration products, kitchen equipment, and other wooden related products in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers melamine face chipboards and melamine faced boards, high pressure laminates, high gloss acrylic panels, PVC panel, laminate flooring, decorative wall panels and wallpapers, veneer products, fire resistant materials, outdoor materials, hardware, and interior doors and panels; and supporting products, including PVC edgeband and hotmelt glue, as well as products for smart homes, and cleaning and protecting interior furniture. It also engages in the provision of installation services; wholesale and retail of interior and interior decoration products; trading in kitchen appliances under Malloca brand name; and trade of real estate, as well as development of residential projects. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Tân Uyên, Vietnam.",
